					<p>The January 2012 issue of the AVRDC’s newsletter details agricultural innovations in Thailand, vegetable processing methods in Mali, the launch of a vegetable research network in southeast Asia, a discussion on (peri-)urban agriculture and, results of seed trials in Papua New Guinea and the LUUNA project in Cameroon, among others. (<a href="http://www.avrdc.org/fileadmin/pdfs/newsletter/13-Jan-2012.pdf%20" target="_blank">AVRDC</a>, 01/2011)</p>
